Àtụ:Infobox musical artist
Kevin Erondu, ónyé a maara nke ọma dị ka K.E
on the Track, bụ ónyé na-emepụta ihe ndekọ America.
A mụrụ Kevin Erondu nà Tampa, Florida. Ọ malitere na Valdosta, Georgia.
bịara na 2009, mgbè o mepụtara otu "Swag Surfin" site n'aka otu rap Fast Life Yungstaz. Egwú ahụ nwetara airplay ma depụta na No
N'afọ 2010, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na abọm izizi nke ónyé na-eti egwu Roscoe Dash bụ Set Ready Go!, ébé o mepụtara 5 n'ime egwu 9, gụnyere egwu abụọ ahụ
"All the Way Turnt Up" e wepụtara na Jenụwarị 2010 wee rụo n'ọkwa nke 46 na Billboard Hot 100. Ọ mepụtara ọtụtụ remixes site n'aka ndị na-ese ihe dịka Ludacris, Fabolous na MGK
sokwa dee ma mepụta egwu nkè abụọ "Show Out", nke e wepụtara n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'otu afọ ahụ.

N'afọ 2011, o mepụtara egwu "You the Boss" nke Rick Ross na Nicki Minaj, nke e wepụtara na mbụ dị ka egwu mbụ site na album studio nke ise nkè Ross God Forgives, I Don't. N'ikpeazụ, e wepụrụ egwu ahụ na ndepụta egwu ikpeazụ, ọ bụ ezie na ọ ruru na No
E debekwara ya na nọmba 33 na nọmba 37, n'otu n'otu, na chaatị Billboard Year-end màkà Hot Rap Songs na Hot R&B / Hip-Hop Songs.
